data.description: Cozy 3 bedroom 1 bath home located in the heart of Delta. Quiet neighborhood w a small town feel. Completely updated! Roof is 4 years old, windows 2020, brand new floors 2021, HVAC 2020, city water. Glistening granite kitchen countertops. Home has a den, perfect for an extra bedroom, office or storage space. Property offers a 2 car detached garage & a completely fenced in backyard with a shed perfect for all of your outdoor gear.  Home warranty included. This one won't last, come see for yourself!
